c: 14
v: 17
t: "yuhawil almutakabir abtlae alqyh waldam waghayr dhlk mimaa ysyl min 'ahl alnaar maratan baed mrt, fala yastatie 'an ybtleh; lqdharth whrarth, wmrarth, wayatih aleadhab alshadid min kuli nawe wamin kuli eudw min jsdh, wama hu bimayit fystryh, walah min baed hdha aleadhab eadhab akhar mwlm"